From 0577b8023148c703cab9107bdbd35623b4be3b38 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Jun 2025 23:59:01 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 02/10] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Add Rx TLV Filter
 Configuration API's for stats mode

With the Filter framework, the following APIs are introduced to configure
Rx TLV filters for stats mode:

Config: Configures TLV filters and stores them in the 2D filter array for
       stats mode.
reset: Clears TLV filters from the 2D filter array for stats mode.
update: Updates the configured TLV filters to HW using the ring selection
        configuration command.
display: Prints the configured TLV filters.

Additinally, this framework supports extedend rx stats mode TLV filter
configuration.

Patch-dependency:
	0405-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Rx-Filter-setp-and-cleanup.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
